videos.description: Dwight Howard snarls and lets out a yell after he powers down an emphatic slam early in the second quarter of Game 4 against the Hawks.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Dwight Howard throws down ferocious jam) 2021/06/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dwight Howard throws down ferocious jam

videos.description: Seth Curry battles against Trae Young and uses a step-back move to create space and lace a jumper from midrange.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Seth Curry hits tough step-back on Trae) 2021/06/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Seth Curry hits tough step-back on Trae

videos.description: John Collins climbs the ladder to grab the Bogdan Bogdanovic miss and stuffs down a dunk to get the Hawks fans juiced.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (John Collins crams down putback jam) 2021/06/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: John Collins crams down putback jam

videos.description: Seth Curry draws the double-team and finds Joel Embiid with a behind-the-back pass to lace a 3-pointer for the Sixers.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Seth Curry sets up Joel Embiid for wide-open 3) 2021/06/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Seth Curry sets up Joel Embiid for wide-open 3

videos.description: Clint Capela hypes up the crowd after he grabs the lob from Trae Young and crams down a dunk to give the Hawks a 94-92 lead in the fourth quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Clint Capela fires up the crowd after big-time dunk in the 4th) 2021/06/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Clint Capela fires up the crowd after big-time dunk in the 4th

videos.description: Trae Young comes up clutch in the final moments of Game 4 as the Hawks rally to squeak away with a 103-100 win over the 76ers to tie the series at 2-2.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Embiid, Curry miss good looks late as Hawks take Game 4) 2021/06/14 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Embiid, Curry miss good looks late as Hawks take Game 4

videos.description: Trae Young finds Onyeka Okongwu rolling to the basket for an emphatic slam to cut the Sixers' lead to 79-77.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Onyeka Okongwu skies to power down a slam) 2021/06/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Onyeka Okongwu skies to power down a slam

videos.description: Trae Young does it again as he records a 25-point, 18-assist double-double to elevate the Hawks to a 103-100 Game 4 win over the 76ers to tie the series at 2-2.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Trae tallies 25 points, 18 assists as Hawks take Game 4 to even series) 2021/06/14 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Trae tallies 25 points, 18 assists as Hawks take Game 4 to even series

videos.description: Kendrick Perkins lauds Trae Young's performance in Game 4 by getting others involved, even when his shot wasn't falling.
